{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八回\"爱是给予\"主要讲述了萧十一郎在酒楼重逢沈璧君的痛苦场景。沈璧君面蒙黑纱，与冰冰发生对峙，冰冰试图揭开她的面纱。萧十一郎认出沈璧君的声音却不敢上前，沈璧君为保护他而假装不认识他，甚至以死相胁。花如玉带沈璧君离开，风四娘因无法动弹也被带走，她默默流泪却无法向萧十一郎表明身份。事后萧十一郎借酒消愁，冰冰冷静分析指出蒙面女子可能是沈璧君的朋友，且被人制住穴道，沈璧君可能是受人威胁才对他冷漠。冰冰鼓励萧十一郎去追寻真爱，并建议向车夫小宋打听马车线索。小宋提供了对方连续三天来的信息，冰冰推断掌柜可能知道对方来历。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你难道要替他们将眼睛挖出来？你是他们的什么人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我不是他们的什么人，可是我宁愿死，也不愿看见这种事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你既然跟他们没有关系，为什么蒙着脸不敢见人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我当然有我的原因。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你不想把你的原因告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "可是我却想看看你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我想你一定是个很好看的女人，因为你的声音也很好听。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你能不能把你脸上的黑纹掀起来，让我看看你？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "难道你连让我看一眼都不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不行就是不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你既然不愿自己掀起这层面纹来，只好让我替你掀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有个人也不知在我面前将你的模样说过多少次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "是谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你应该知道是谁说的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你……你也知道我是谁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你当然就是武林中的第一美人沈璧君。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你怎么知道我是谁的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你若不是沈璧君，他又怎么会变成这样子？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你错了，我既不姓沈，也不是沈璧君。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "谁认得沈璧君？谁认得那种又血又笨的女人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你难道一定要我掀起你的面纹来，你才肯承认？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "拿开你的手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你只要敢碰一碰我，我就死在你面前。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你……你……你难道已不认得我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不认得你，我根本就不认得你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我们走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你瞪着他干什么？难道你也想杀了他？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "text": "我们为什么还不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你在流泪？你为什么要流泪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你是谁？为什么要为别人的事流泪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送二十斤酒来，要最好的酒。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "也许那个人真的不是沈姓娘。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你用不着安慰我，我并不难受。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我只不过想痛痛快快的喝顿酒而已，我已有很久未醉过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是，欧阳兄弟刚才已悄悄溜了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们也许还会再来的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你怕他们又约了帮手来找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我当然不怕，半个喝醉了的萧十一郌，也已足够对付两百个清醒的欧阳文件兄弟了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "说得好，当浮三大白。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我只不过在奇怪，另外一个蒙着黑纹的女人是谁呢？她为什么要流泪？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你怎么看见她在流泪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我看得见，她脸上的那层面纹都已被眼泪湿透。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "也许她病了，一个人在病得很压害时，往往会流泪的，尤其是女人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是我知道她并没有病。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "她已病得连路都不能走，你还说她没有病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那不是病。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "不是病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "病重的人，一定四肢发软，才走不动路，可是她四肢上的关节，却好像很难弯曲，全身都好像是僵硬的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你实在比我细心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "莫忘记，我本来就是个女神童。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以我看她不是真的病了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "莫非她是被人制住了穴道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "你看她是为了什么而流泪的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "很可能是为了你们的事，为了沈璧君。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "谁会为了我们的事而流泪？别人连开心都来不及，我就算死在路上，也绝没有人会掉一滴眼泪的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "至少我……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是她却掉了眼泪，所以我认为她不但认得你们，而且一定对沈姓娘很关心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "也许她是为了别的事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "刚才这里并没别的事能令人流泪的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "所以你认为她是沈璧君的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "一定是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "她既然被人制住了穴道，沈璧君当然也很可能受了那个人的威胁的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以她刚才会对你那样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "也许她并不是真的想对我那么无情的，我刚才为什么偏偏没有想到？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为你心里有条毒蛇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "毒蛇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "怀疑和嫉妒，就是你心里的毒蛇。你心里还是忘不了她的，否则你也不会怀疑她，不会嫉妒那个男人了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你既然忘不了她，为什么不去找她呢？现在就去找，一定还来得及。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "我怎么找？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "她们是坐马车走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "是辆什么样的马车？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是辆很新的黑漆马车，拉车的马也是全身漆黑，看不见杂色，马车的主人，一定是很有身份的人，这么样的马车并不难找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是我们最好还是先去问问我们的车夫小宋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "车夫和车夫总是比较容易交朋友的，他们在外面等主人的时候，闲着没事做，话也总是特别多，所以小宋知道的也可能比我们多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_song",
      "speaker_name": "小宋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个车夫是个很古怪的人，我们在聊天的时候，他总是板着脸，连听都不愿听，别人要跟他搭设，他也总是不理不督，就好像有人欠他三百吁钱没还一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_song",
      "speaker_name": "小宋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三天来，他们总是很早就来了，很晚才回去，好像在等人一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_song",
      "text": "他们已接连来了三天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_song",
      "speaker_name": "小宋",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_song",
      "text": "他们已很引人注意，若是一连来了三天，这地方的掌柜就很可能知道他们的来历了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    }
  ],
